---
alwaysApply: false
description: Enriches graph with external facts and evidence
globs: got/**/*.py
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Search for information relevant to existing nodes
- Create FACT or CONCEPT nodes with EVIDENCE_FOR / EVIDENCE_AGAINST / EXPLAINS
- Annotate sources in metadata

**Constraints:**
- Only creates nodes and edges; no structural validation
- Uses epistemic RelationType (EVIDENCE_FOR, STRENGTHENS, WEAKENS)

**Pattern:** Node(FACT, concept="...", metadata={"source": "..."}) + Edge(EVIDENCE_FOR)

**Dependencies:** graph-expander, got.domain.ops